title: Kenyon Martin Interview and More

description:
Friday 6/23- Today on the show we had Kenya Martin, former NBA player come by, where he spoke about being apart of Ice Cube's Big 3 League, his ex Trina and more. Also, its Freaky Freaky Friday so we took a clip from when comedian Tiffany Haddish was here and spoke about her horrible experience with a not so average size penis, so we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners had a bad experience with a big penis.
